quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,23,"Innee wajadtu imraatan tamlikuhum waootiyatmin kulli shay-in walaha AAarshun AAatheem"
  27,24,"Wajadtuha waqawmaha yasjudoonalishshamsi min dooni Allahi wazayyana lahumu ashshaytanuaAAmalahum fasaddahum AAani assabeeli fahumla yahtadoon"
  27,25,"Alla yasjudoo lillahi allatheeyukhriju alkhabaa fee assamawati wal-ardiwayaAAlamu ma tukhfoona wama tuAAlinoon"
  27,26,"Allahu la ilaha illahuwa rabbu alAAarshi alAAatheem"
  27,27,"Qala sananthuru asadaqtaam kunta mina alkathibeen"
  27,28,"Ithhab bikitabee hathafaalqih ilayhim thumma tawalla AAanhum fanthurmatha yarjiAAoon"
  27,29,"Qalat ya ayyuha almalaoinnee olqiya ilayya kitabun kareem"
  27,30,"Innahu min sulaymana wa-innahu bismiAllahi arrahmani arraheem"
  27,31,"Alla taAAloo AAalayya wa/tooneemuslimeen"
  27,32,"Qalat ya ayyuha almalaoaftoonee fee amree ma kuntu qatiAAatan amran hattatashhadoon"
  27,33,"Qaloo nahnu oloo quwwatinwaoloo ba/sin shadeedin wal-amru ilayki fanthureematha ta/mureen"
  27,34,"Qalat inna almulooka ithadakhaloo qaryatan afsadooha wajaAAaloo aAAizzata ahlihaathillatan wakathalika yafAAaloon"
  27,35,"Wa-innee mursilatun ilayhim bihadiyyatin fanathiratunbima yarjiAAu almursaloon"
